# StreamPay™ Contribution Guide

Thank you for considering contributing to StreamPay™, the revolutionary payment platform built on the Solana and FUEL blockchain platforms. We welcome contributions from developers, designers, testers, and anyone interested in helping us achieve our vision of simplifying financial interactions within blockchain ecosystems.

